<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Playground!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @resource.name || @email %>!</h2>
      
      <p>
        Thank you for signing up for Playground by Flukebase. We're excited to have you join our community!
      </p>
      
      <p>
        To complete your registration and verify your email address, please click the button below:
      </p>
      
      <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeeba; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p style="color: #856404; margin: 0; font-weight: bold;">⚠️ Important: Account Activation Required</p>
        <p style="color: #856404; margin-top: 8px;">
          You must activate your account within <strong>24 hours</strong> of registration or it will be automatically deleted for security reasons.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <%= link_to 'Confirm My Account', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token), class: "button" %>
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Once your email is confirmed, you'll have full access to all our language learning features:
      </p>
      
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Realtime AI Conversations</strong> - Practice speaking with our AI language partners</li>
        <li><strong>Audio Transcription</strong> - Get detailed feedback on your pronunciation</li>
        <li><strong>Practice History</strong> - Track your progress over time</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics</strong> - Gain insights into your learning journey</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Happy learning!<br>
        The Flukebase Team
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Flukebase. All rights reserved.<br>
        This email was sent to <%= @email %>
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
        <small>Account Policy: Accounts that remain inactive for 30 consecutive days after activation will be automatically deleted.</small>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
